These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, dog, turtle, mouse
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the dog is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the mouse##7
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | turtle | dog | mouse | rat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, artichoke, peas, plum
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person eating peas is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person eating cabbage##7
3. the person eating peas is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating plum##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | cabbage | plum | peas | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, watermelon, tomato, blueberry
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person eating blueberry is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person eating watermelon##7
3. the person eating tomato is somewhere to the right of the person eating blueberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | cucumber | watermelon | blueberry | tomato |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, car, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the helicopter##7
2. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
3. the person driving the van is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | car | van | skateboard | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, adventure, family
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching family movies##2
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
4. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching family movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | musical | disaster | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, british, malaysian, french
1. the egyptian is somewhere between the french and the british##7
2. the malaysian is somewhere between the egyptian and the french##7
3. the malaysian is on the left or right of the french##3
4. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the french##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | french | malaysian | egyptian | british |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, milk, water
1. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking soy-milk##7
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##7
3. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water | milk | juice |

