.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bike, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person driving the motorbike##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | motorbike | boat | roller | bike |

